acknowledgements.ack:
Fleet-pause SOP: state.pause_fleet(...) + commit BEFORE branch checkout;
state.resume_fleet(...) (NOT unpause_fleet) + commit as LAST action.
Unpause commit message: "chore(ops): unpause fleet -- Stage 6 Phase 7 complete;
Stage 6.7.5 CLOSED" — record the closure milestone in the commit message.
